reviewText: I think everyone would benefit from watching this series. Chip shares powerful insights about what makes us tick.

We love this program. Great for those who might need guidance along with those who don't! There's always room for a person to improve and this is a great way to start. Have bought this for others, so we do recommend this DVD with Study Guide.
Greatly appreciate the rapid delivery and the availability of used items which become an affordable resource for families! Thank you again! ;-)
